quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  10,53,"Sano ŵanganyao akum’busyaga (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) kuti: “Nambo yalakweyi yakuona?” Jilani: “Eee! Ngwalumbila Ambuje ŵangu, chisimu yalakweyi yakuona, soni jenumanja nganim’ba iyyilepelekasyisye.”"
  10,54,"Soni ingaŵe kuti mundu jwalijose juŵatesile lupuso jwaakwete yosope ya pa chilambo, jukasachilile kuja kuliombolela nayo, soni tachiligamba chamuntima ndema jatachiyiona ilagasyo, ni kuchilamulidwa chilikati chao mwachilungamiko, soni ŵanganyao ngasatendedwa lupuso"
  10,55,"Manyililani yanti chisimu Allah ni Nsyene yosope yaili kumawunde ni petaka. Manyililani yanti chisimu chilanga cha Allah ni chakuonaonape, nambo kuti ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ngaakumanyilila"
  10,56,"Jwalakwe akupeleka umi ni kupeleka chiwa, soni Kukwakwe chinchiuchisyidwa"
  10,57,"E jenumanja achinaŵandu! Pamasile pachim’bichilile chamuko (Qur’an) kuumila kwa M’mbuje gwenu, ni chakuposya (ulwele) wauli m’mitima mwenu, nambo soni chongolo ni chanasa ku ŵakulupilila"
  10,58,"Jilani: “Mwaukoto wa Allah ni chanasa Chakwe (apatile yalakweyi), basi kwaligongo lyele asangalale.” Yalakweyo niyambone nnope kupunda (ipanje) yaakusonganganya"
  10,59,"Jilani: “Ana nkuyiona uli mu lisiki lyaatulwisye Allah kukwenu, basi jenumanja nillitesile line mu lyalakwelyo kuŵa lya haraam line ni kuŵa lya halaal.” Jilani: “Ana Allah ni jwanchisisye (yalakweyi) kapena nkunsepela Allah unami?”"
  10,60,"Ana nganisyo sya aŵala ŵaakunsepela Allah unami sili syantiuli ya lisiku lya Kiyama (akuganisya yanti tachikulupuka ku ipotesi)? Chisimu Allah akwete ukoto kwa ŵandu, nambo kuti ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ŵangatogolela"
  10,61,"Ni ngankuŵaga (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) m’masengo galigose, soni ngankusoomaga mwalakwemo chilichose cha m’Qur’an, soni (jenumanja achinaŵandu) ngankupanganyaga masengo galigose, ikaŵeje Uwwe tukuŵaga Mboni pa jenumanja ndema jankujijilika nago, soni ngachikasasisika kwa Ambuje ŵenu (chindu) chausito wanti mpela lunyilili pasi kapena kwinani, soni namuno chamwana nnope kupunda chalakwecho kapena chakulilapo niikaŵeje chili m’chitabu chakusalichisya (chilichose Al-Lauh-Al-Mahfûz)"
  10,62,Manyililani yanti chisimu isyoŵe ya Allah ngasiyiŵa ni woga soni ngasiyiŵa yakudandaula
  10,63,Aŵala ŵaŵakulupilile ni kuŵa ni woga (wakun’jogopa Allah)
  10,64,"Akwete kupata ŵanganyao abali jakusengwasya pa umi wa duniya (kupitila mu sagamisi syambone), ni ku Akhera (chakapate yambone), pangali galausya maloŵe ga Allah, kwalakweko ni kupunda kwekulungwa nnope"
  10,65,"Sano gakan’dandaulikasya maloŵe gao (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), chisimu machili ni uchimbichimbi yosope yene ya Allah, Jwalakwe ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakumanyilila nnope"
  10,66,"Manyililani yanti chisimu Allah ni Nsyene (iwumbe yosope) yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka, sano aŵala ŵaakuiŵendaga yinepe yangaŵaga Allah ngaakuikuyaga yakuiwanganya (ni Allah), ngakukuyaga ikaŵeje liganichisyape, soni nganaŵa ŵanganyao ikaŵeje nkusepelela unami basi"
  10,67,"Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwam’bichile chilo kuti ntulalilejemo, soni muusi (autesile) kuŵa wakuloleka (yindu kukwenu), chisimu mu yalakweyo mwana ilosyo kwa ŵandu ŵakupikanichisya"
  10,68,"Ŵanganyao akutiji: “Allah alitendele mwanache.” Kuswejela ni Kwakwe, Jwalakwe ni Jwakusichila kusyene, iŵele Yakwe (yosope) yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka. Nganinkola ŵanganyammwe umboni uliose pa yalakweyi. Ana nkum’bechetela Allah yangankuimanyilila"
  10,69,"Jilani: “Chisimu aŵala ŵaakunsepela Allah unami nganaŵa apundile.”"
  10,70,"Kusengwa (kwandema jannono chakupate) pa duniya, kaneko Kukwetu ni kwakuujila kwao, soni ni tuchapa kupasya ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope ligongo lya ukafili wao uŵaliji nkutenda"